  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Aarti, I'm Miss Maya. Honestly, I love how hopeful you sound about trying new things, even if they’re a little scary! Did you decide to bake that chocolate cake yet?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yes, I baked the cake! It was not easy, but I managed. My sister said it was \"badi acchi\" (very good). I want to try making a new recipe with bananas next. How about you, Maya—do you enjoy cooking?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds lovely, 'badi acchi' is high praise from family! Bananas in the next recipe sounds fun. I enjoy cooking in small ways, what kind of banana recipe are you thinking of?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hmm... maybe a banana bread? Or perhaps a banana lassi for a change. I get bored with the same things. But I’m not sure how to balance the sweetness. Do you think cardamom would work in banana bread?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That’s a great idea! Cardamom adds warmth and fits well with bananas. I’d say give it a try, a little goes a long way. What’s your plan for the sweetness?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I think I'll use honey instead of sugar. It's healthier and gives a nice flavor. But maybe add a pinch of cardamom with it? I'll tell you how it turns out. For sweetness balance, maybe half honey and half something else?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Good idea, honey and cardamom pair well. A mix of honey and a touch of sugar could work too. I’ll look forward to hearing how it turns out!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I think I will try 2/3 honey and 1/3 sugar. Also, maybe add a tsp of cinnamon with the cardamom? It could give a nice twist. Need to study now, but I’ll bake it tomorrow! Talk to you later, Maya!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Got it, 2/3 honey, 1/3 sugar, and cinnamon with cardamom. Sounds like a winning mix! Study well, and do share how it tastes tomorrow. Talk soon!"
    }
  ],
